Business Brief -- Pittway Corp.:
   Seaquist to Acquire Pfeiffer
   And Be Spun Off in Pact
Pittway wouldn't disclose further details of the plan.
   The Chicago maker of burglar and fire alarm equipment and
home security items said the spinoff and combination are
subject to receipt of a favorable ruling on the spinoff from
the Internal Revenue Service and other conditions, including
a definitive agreement and regulatory approvals. The
transactions are expected to be completed by early 1993.